# Styling and Component Patterns

## Component Structure
The landing page is organized in [src/pages/landing/index.tsx](mdc:src/pages/landing/index.tsx) with these sections:
- `Header` - Fixed header with logo
- `Hero` - Main hero section with title and CTA
- `WhyUs` - Introduction section
- `Features` - Feature cards grid
- `Pricing` - Pricing information
- `FAQ` - Accordion-style FAQ section
- `Contact` - Final CTA section
- `Footer` - Footer with copyright

## Styling Approach
- **Theme Colors**: Defined in [src/theme/theme.ts](mdc:src/theme/theme.ts)
  - Dark navy background (`#19181f`)
  - Olive green accents (`#97823e`, `#545034`)
  - Terracotta buttons (`#d38c57`)
  - Light peach highlights (`#f1c67a`)
- **CSS File**: [src/pages/landing/LandingPage.css](mdc:src/pages/landing/LandingPage.css) - All landing page styles
- Uses CSS custom properties (CSS variables) for theming
- Dark theme with glassmorphism effects on cards

## Component Patterns

### FAQ Accordion
- Uses React `useState` to manage open/closed state
- Only one FAQ item can be open at a time
- Arrow indicators (▶ when closed, ▼ when open)
- Smooth animations for expand/collapse

### Feature Cards
- Grid layout with `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr))`
- Hover effects with transform and border color changes
- Transparent backgrounds with subtle borders

### Responsive Design
- Mobile breakpoint at 768px
- Grid layouts collapse to single column on mobile
- Font sizes scale down appropriately

## Styling Guidelines
- Use CSS custom properties from theme for colors
- Maintain consistent spacing using theme spacing values
- Use em dashes (—) for better readability in text
- Keep grammar and capitalization consistent
- Use semicolons for compound sentences in FAQ answers
